<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Team Invite</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .logo img{
            background-color: #ffffff;
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 20px;
            color: #1d1d1d;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #2AAD8E;
        }
        .content h3 {
            color: #1d1d1d;
        }
        .content h4 {
            color: #1d1d1d;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #2AAD8E;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1d1d1d;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .social-icons img {
            width: 24px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 5px;
        }
        
        /* Responsive styles */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .logo img {
                width: 100px; /* Adjust based on your logo size */
            }
            .button {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 15px 0;
            }
            .social-icons img {
                width: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <!-- Include your logo image here -->
            <img src="https://app.smythos.dev/img/smythos-logo.png" alt="SmythOS Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Ready to Join a Winning Team?</h2>
            <h3>Congratulations<% if (invitee?.name) { %>, <%= invitee.name %><% } %>!</h3>
            <p>Here is your exclusive invitation<% if (inviter?.name) { %> from <strong><%= inviter.name %></strong><% } %> to join <strong style="color: #2AAD8E; font-weight: bold;"><%= team?.name %> team</strong>.</p>
            <p>Don't miss the opportunity to collaborate and build powerful AI agents together with a team.</p>
            <h4>‚è∞üëáAccept your invitation before it expires!</h4>
            <a href="<%= config.FRONTEND_BASE_URL %>/teams/accept-invitation/<%= invitation.code %>" class="button">Accept Team Invite</a>
            <p>Once you accept, you'll be officially part of the team and be able to collaborate with your team members. Your role and permissions will be defined by your team admin.</p>
            <p>We're excited to see what powerful AI agents you'll build with your team!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Join our community:</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <!-- Include your LinkedIn and Discord icons here -->
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/smythos/mycompany/" target="_blank">
                    <!--   <img src="path-to-linkedin-icon.png" alt="LinkedIn" /> -->
                    Linkedin
                  </a>
                  <a href="https://discord.gg/pF8GSzbBEM" target="_blank">
                    <!-- <img src="path-to-discord-icon.png" alt="Discord" /> -->
                    Discord
                  </a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="mailto:support@inkco.co">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
            <p>¬© 2024 SmythOS an INK Content, Inc. company   ‚Ä¢   1321 Upland Dr. 1036   ‚Ä¢   Houston, TX 77339</p>
            <a href="https://smythos.com" target="_blank">www.smythos.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
